This document should serve following purposes:
   * this is the central documentation hub for admin documentation
   * it should say what an OSG resource is, what a compute element and what a storage resource is
   * show a map of OSG resources
   * provide contact information for administrators
   * link to OIM
   * link to all relevant OSG documentation for grid administrators
%ENDCOLOR%

